{"title": "Spirit of Christ", "description": "Shortly after his ascension to heaven, Jesus sent the Holy Spirit, the Promise of the Father, to indwell, comfort, teach, strengthen and encourage believers.  Andrew Murray observes in his preface that while our creed on the Holy Spirit is orthodox and scriptural, his presence and power in the life of believers, in the ministry of the word, and in the witness of the Church to the world, is not what the word promises or God\u2019s plan requires.<br><br>\r\n\r\nIn this little book consisting of 31 daily devotions, Murray guides us through the many ways in which the Holy Spirit works in the lives of Christians to bring glory to God and to help us live truly transformed lives.<br>\r\n - Summary by Christopher Smith", "duration": 46086, "language": "English", "authors": [{"id": "2839", "name": "Andrew Murray"}], "coverArt": "https://archive.org/download/spiritofchrist_2412_librivox/spiritofchrist_2412.jpg", "copyright_year": "1888", "genres": ["Christianity - Other"], "supporters": [{"role": "Read by", "name": "Christopher Smith"}, {"role": "Book Coordinator", "name": "Christopher Smith"}, {"role": "Meta Coordinator", "name": "TriciaG"}, {"role": "Proof Listener", "name": "Guster"}], "sections": [{"section": 0, "title": "Preface", "readers": [7424], "path": "https://www.archive.org/download/spiritofchrist_2412_librivox/spiritofchrist_00_murray_64kb.mp3", "duration": 859}, {"section": 1, "title": "First Day: A New Spirit, and God's Spirit", "readers": [7424], "path": "https://www.archive.org/download/spiritofchrist_2412_librivox/spiritofchrist_01_murray_64kb.mp3", "duration": 1091}, {"section": 2, "title": "Second Day: The Baptism of the Spirit", "readers": [7424], "path": "https://www.archive.org/download/spiritofchrist_2412_librivox/spiritofchrist_02_murray_64kb.mp3", "duration": 1002}, {"section": 3, "title": "Third Day: Worship in the Spirit", "readers": [7424], "path": "https://www.archive.org/download/spiritofchrist_2412